Class ParsedSourceImpl

java.lang.Object
  testsgen.wttools.ParsedSourceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, ParsedSourceIfc
Direct Known Subclasses:
ParsedSourceImpl
public class ParsedSourceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParsedSourceIfc

ParsedSourceImpl.java contains implementation of ParsedSourceIfc interface. It contains methods for accessing all source elements.

This implementation (and interface) is class oriented. It means that whole idea and desing is for class processing. Additionally it assumes only one class in each file. This assumption is good for processing java sources but should be modified for processing other languages sources.
